   <section id="about-our-environmental-goals" class="why_matter content-paragraph paragraph-container">
    <div class="species_image species_image_reverse">
        <picture >
                <img loading="lazy" src="/sites/default/files/styles/content_slide_image/public/2017-06/Mountaineers_Cairngorms.jpg?h=82f92a78&amp;itok=zzH7ejjn" width="1000" height="600" alt="" title="Mountaineers in Cairngorms winter" class="image-style-content-slide-image" />




        </picture>

                <div class="copyright--image">© Global Warming Images / WWF</div>
            </div>
    <div class="content content--padded content_reverse">
            <h3>

<div class="field field--display_title">
  <h2>About our environmental goals</h2>
</div>
</h3>
            <div class="rich-text-wrapper">
          <p><span lang="EN-US">Our mission is to create a world where people and wildlife can thrive together. </span><span>'Walking the talk’ is essential to achieving this. Our responsibility does not end with influencing others to safeguard the natural world through their key decisions – we must also play our part, reducing our own impacts as well as inspiring others to do the same.</span> We've come a long way since our first environmental policy was launched in 1989, but we'll always be working to improve our environmental performance.</p>
<p>In 2008 we became&nbsp;certified to the environmental management standard ISO 14001 and have upheld this certification every year since.&nbsp;Most recently, we moved our head office&nbsp;to a bespoke designed building - The Living Planet Centre - which was awarded a top rating of 'Outstanding' by BREEAM; an internationally recognised&nbsp;environmental assessment for buildings.&nbsp;</p>
<p>Below is a summary of our key areas of environmental performance, for more details about how we set targets for these areas please read our Environmental Goals. Each year we publish an Environmental Report which summarises our performance against our targets, these can be downloaded below.</p>


      </div>
              

          <div class="btn-wrap">
                          
                   

     <div class="btn-wrap--item">
     <a href="http://assets.wwf.org.uk/custom/stories/lpc/"  class="btn anchor_link  btn--white" ga-on="click" ga-event-category="CTAButton" ga-event-action="click - http://assets.wwf.org.uk/custom/stories/lpc/" ga-event-label=" About our environmental goals  The story of the Living Planet Centre">
         The story of the Living Planet Centre
     </a>
     </div>

     
     
               
                   

     <div class="btn-wrap--item">
     <a href="https://www.wwf.org.uk/sites/default/files/2023-07/WWF-UK%20Environmental%20Goals%20to%202030%20%282023%20update%29_0.pdf"  class="btn anchor_link  btn--white" ga-on="click" ga-event-category="CTAButton" ga-event-action="click - https://www.wwf.org.uk/sites/default/files/2023-07/WWF-UK%20Environmental%20Goals%20to%202030%20%282023%20update%29_0.pdf" ga-event-label=" About our environmental goals  Environmental Goals until 2030">
         Environmental Goals until 2030
     </a>
     </div>

     
     
      
     </div>
          </div>
</section>


